name: The Archer Chair - Davidson
description: The Archer is an inviting seating solution whose tasteful design evokes a solidity and dignified assurance. The softly curved backrest, alongside its beech frame, flaring slightly at each corner, offers both elegance and optimum comfort. The supportive and comfortable frame has been finished in the inky tones of sycamore black, sitting in eye-catching contrast to the upholstery. A customisable chair, the Archer can be upholstered in any fabric or leather to suit any luxury interior.
